Share information
Cube Storage Pioneers

Little Robots, Big Business

Since its inception in 1996, AutoStore™ has worked to improve warehouse efficiency. Today, the company’s key value proposition is to deliver an easy-to-use software powered cubic automatic storage and retrieval ecosystem.

The AutoStore solution is modular and flexible, and can automate any warehouse. The system offers a superior customer value proposition across operating metrics, ESG scores, and customer economics.
‍

View video to learn more

entry.content: ... that conservation in Indonesia had little local support after independence because it was associated with the Dutch colonial period?

entry.title: Tilted Towers (Wikipedia — did you know?)
entry.content: ... that Fortnite's Tilted Towers was described by critics as the equivalent of "psychological torture" and being "dropped into a meat grinder"?

entry.title: Elijah Hewson' (Wikipedia — did you know?)

entry.content: ... that the Platt Report was commissioned to improve British nursing education, as at the time up to 50 per cent of trainee nurses failed to qualify?

entry.content: ... that in 2022, Julia Dorsey helped North Carolina win a national lacrosse championship and reach the national soccer final?
